    <title>XENSIV™ PAS CO2 (1st generation) release notes</title>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This library provides functions for interfacing with the XENSIV™ PAS CO2 sensor.</para>
<sect2 id="md__r_e_l_e_a_s_e_1autotoc_md7">
<title>What&apos;s included?</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>APIs for configuring the XENSIV™ PAS CO2 sensor</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>APIs for reading CO2 PPM value out of the XENSIV™ PAS CO2 sensor</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="md__r_e_l_e_a_s_e_1autotoc_md8">
<title>What Changed?</title>
<sect3 id="md__r_e_l_e_a_s_e_1autotoc_md9">
<title>v1.0.0</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>New API</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Added support for UART communication interface</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Added support for using with HAL v1 or v2 </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="md__r_e_l_e_a_s_e_1autotoc_md10">
<title>v0.6.0</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Baseline offset and forced compensation calibration configurable</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Pressure reference can be configured from external source </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="md__r_e_l_e_a_s_e_1autotoc_md11">
<title>v0.5.0</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Initial release</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect3>
</sect2>
